Title: [BOUNTY]BUILDERIUM.IO - FULLY AUTOMATED BOUNTYSUITE.com! JOIN NOW!
Body: EVERY BOUNTY TASK HAS MOVED TO AUTOMATED BOUNTYSUITE.COM WEBSITE:  https://www.bountysuite.com/bounty-programs/builderium.html    BUILDERIUM    Website | Telegram | Twitter| Whitepaper  What is Builderium?  Builderium is a platform connecting construction workers and contractors clients. At present, there are three pronounced problems with the construction industry. Increasing competition makes finding clients increasingly difficult. Constructions workers can find job offers they are looking for in their living area. Clients are not sure about the quality of construction workers they are about to hire. Also, the price may be to steep for a project. Builderium platform aims to solve all those problems.  PROMOTE BUILDERIUM AND EARN BUILD TOKENS!  Please use this form for your issues. Answers will be available on the spreadsheet in the answers tab. In this way we will ensure transparency.   This bounty campaign will last for12 WEEKS.. The total of Bounty bonus to be paid to the participants is 3% of total token sold.       Bounty Allocation  Signature Bounty 45% Youtube/Blog/Article 20% Twitter Bounty 15% Translation Bounty 10% Telegram Bounty 10%  General Rules  First week of the bounty campaign will start on the 16th of July 2018, Monday. Signature stakes will be distributed weekly. Other stakes will be calculated end of the campaign. Stakes earned during the bounty campaign will be credited to the participants’ accounts within a week after the closing of the Bounty Campaign. As a reward for the bounty activities, you will receive BUILD tokens. The tokens are allocated gradually to your wallet after the end of the ICO. We reserve our right to eliminate you if we think you haven't been honest with your work. We reserve the right to change bounty campaign rules. Follower/Friend number cannot be change while campaign. Using multi-accounts, cheating, using someone else to do the work and spamming or any kind of unethical behaviour when participating to one of the campaigns is not allowed and will get you disqualified from all bounties. Reward system may change if we do not reach desired number of participants.   Signature Campaign   Weekly Rewards:   Jr. Member: 0,5 stake per week Member: 0,75 stake per week Full Member: 1 stake per week (+0.25 stake for avatar, text) Senior Member: 1,5 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar, text) Hero Member: 2 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar, text) Legendary: 2,5 stakes per week (+0,25 stake for avatar, text)   Signature Campaign Rules:  Participants must be at least a Jr.Member, do not apply if you are not at least a Jr.Member. Multiple accounts will be banned if spotted. Spam and burst posts are not allowed. We expect you to post 10 constructive posts per week. 5 of these posts can be in local boards. Posts should not be made in bounties, off topic, archival, meta and politic sections. You will have to keep wearing our signature, avatar and personal text until the end of the campaign. We will single handedly check every post of every participant. We will check your previous posts whether it is of quality or not. If your rank changes during the campaign, please use issue form to notify the Bounty Manager. Accounts with negative trust from DT-2 or DR-1 are not allowed to enrol. Do not fill the form without wearing our signature, or you will be rejected.  Application Form: https://www.bountysuite.com/bounty-programs/builderium.html Spreadsheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/121Vr0VbujikgJmmtCh1hw0X4r8KoX1ZN5DfxJQsYS90/edit?usp=sharing  Avatar, personal text and signature codes are on the second post of this thread.   Youtube/Blog/Article Campaign   You must have at least 250 organic subscribers on YouTube. Your YouTube video must be at least 2 minutes long. The video should be descriptive. Those in the form of musical presentation will not be accepted. Speech must be made by a real person, videos edited with the help of voice synthesizers will not be accepted. The video has to be of good quality. The website / blog where you post the content must be at least 3 months old. Your Medium/Steem.it/Youtube or any other free blogging blog page should have at least 250 followers. Your article / blog post / video must be public. Content at websites and blogs where the number of views is not transparent will not be accepted(Blogspot, Wordpress, etc.). Your article / blog post has to be original, of good writing quality, and at least 500 words. Your article / blog post / video should have links to the YRC token website, ANN thread, and whitepaper. If you are submitting a website, it should have good traffic. Participant can submit maximum 2 contents. More than 2 applications will not be accepted. The same content post can only be posted once. Do not apply the same content on different websites, it will be declined. Applicant must indicate his/her ETH address under the video or article she/he sends. Only original work is accepted! Copying parts of the website / paper or using the work of someone else will disqualify your work(s). Contents at websites that do not appear in Similarweb analysis will not be accepted. We have strict rules to make sure we reward quality works from known people. They will also be satisfied with the reward as each participant will be hand picked. You will get stakes based on the quality and popularity of your work, reviewed at the end of the campaign. We also accept ICO Rating - Listing websites. Stakes are based on the quality and popularity gained from the content. Articles/videos etc. will be evaluated according to the number of views and visitors. In terms of quality, publications that are at a higher level than others can be additionally rewarded with 1 to 10 stakes. Content that does not satisfy any of the rules will not be accepted. You will be able to get 1, 3, 5, 7, or 10 stake(s) depending on the number of visitors/ views/ similarweb points, and you will be able to get 1, 3, 5, 7, or 10 stake(s) depending on the content quality. At the end of the campaign, the stakes for quality and stakes for popularity will be combined, and you can get up to 20 stakes in total.   0 - 50 views l 0 stake 51 - 150 views l 1 stakes 151 - 250 views l 3 stakes 251 - 500 views l 5 stakes 501 - 1000 views l 7 stakes >1001 views l 10 stakes    0 - 250.000 points l 10 stakes 250.000 - 1.000.000 points l 7 stakes 1.000.000 - 5.000.000 points l 5 stakes 5.000.000 - 15.000.000 points l 3 stakes 15.000.000 - 30.000.000 points l 1 stakes >30.000.000 points l 0 stake  Submit your publications to https://www.bountysuite.com/bounty-programs/builderium.html Spreadsheet: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/121Vr0VbujikgJmmtCh1hw0X4r8KoX1ZN5DfxJQsYS90/edit?usp=sharing      Twitter Campaign  All participants must follow our official twitter account to be eligible for the Twitter campaign. . You need to have at least 250 real followers if your account focuses on crypto/blockchain/decentralization, or 1000 real followers if it does not. You can report maximum 1 Retweet and Like a day, and 3 Retweets and Likes per week. To help with this, we will add weekly rows on the Twitter spreadsheet.
